channel.title: Free Model Download WebSites
channel.description:
In this thread, there are some very cool websites were you can download some very cool models. It took me awhile to find all these sites.
This doesnt mean you can bring models from these sites to here, and say you made them. In other words: Do Not Leech These Models.
Here are the sites
This site is more for decoritives, furniture, sculptures ect. [url=http://www.3dmodelfree.com/3dmodel/list408-3.htm]3D Model Free[/url]
This site has everything. This would be best for weapons. [url=http://artist-3d.com/]Artist-3D[/url]
This site has some random stuff. [url=http://cg-india.com/cgblog_3dmodels.html]CG-India[/url]
This site is for furniture [url=http://www.mr-cad.com/Free-3D-Models-c-19-1.html]Mr. Furniture[/url]
This site is has alot of stuff, including characters from shows, weapons, and vehicles. [url=http://www.3dvalley.com/3d-models]3D Valley[/url]
This site has alot of stuff. You need to register to download models [url=http://www.3dxtras.com/]3D Xtras[/url]
This site has alot of stuff. This would be good for holiday stuff, and electronics. [url=http://www.3dxo.com/page/36.htm]3D Xo[/url]
This site good for scenery, and people. [url=http://www.klicker.de/models.html]Klicker[/url]
This site is good for furniture, and cars. [url=http://archive3d.net/]Archive 3D[/url]
This site is the NASA model site. [url=http://www.nasa.gov/multimedia/3d_resources/3d-models-index.html]NASA Models[/url]
This site is good for insects, and space ships. [url=http://www.digitalanimators.com/HTM/Resources/3dModels/3dModelsMain.htm]Digital Animators[/url]
This is a cool site. It has over 3,00 models. [url=http://www.cadalyst.net/images/samples.html]Cadalyst[/url]
Thats all i have for now. When i come across another cool site, i will add.
